OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports Journalist
OL,8,FJennifer Buck spoke to students and
OL,9,Fparents ahead of the High Court making
OL,10,Fits final decision.
OL,12,FThe future of a performing arts school
OL,13,Fis in the hands of the High Court,
OL,14,Ffollowing protests from students,
OL,15,Fparents and teachers.
OL,17,FThe Liverpool Institute for Performing
OL,18,FArts (LIPA) announced on Friday 27
OL,19,FFebruary that the school will shut
OL,20,Fdown at the end of the academic year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
