PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FThe school, which opened in 2014, is
OL,8,Ffor children from four to 16 and is
OL,9,Fnot connected to the college of the
OL,10,Fsame name founded by Sir Paul
OL,11,FMcCartney.
OL,13,FLIPA faces a financial deficit,
OL,14,Ffalling pupil numbers and in its most
OL,15,Frecent OFSTED report it was rated
OL,16,Finadequate but teachers and parents
OL,17,Fsay many improvements have been made
OL,18,Fsince then.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FYear 10 student Alice Mather-
OL,8,FMulholland is staying at the school
OL,9,Funtil a decision is made, despite many
OL,10,Fof her friends having already left.
OL,12,FShe said: "The teachers are still
OL,13,Ftrying, they're trying to make it as
OL,14,Fnormal as it can be no matter how many
OL,15,Fpeople have left, whether there's five
OL,16,Fpeople left in your class or 15.
OL,18,F"You can still see that everyone is
OL,19,Ftrying really really hard to keep it
OL,20,Fopen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FDouglas Trafford - another Year 10
OL,8,Fstudent who has chosen to stay at LIPA
OL,9,Funtil a final decision is made - said:
OL,10,F"You've got to carry on, you've got to
OL,11,Fpretend nothing else has happened.
OL,13,F"The classes are small but the
OL,14,Fteachers are highly focussed on what
OL,15,Fwe need."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
