PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FAlthough a lot of parents have moved
OL,8,Ftheir children to other schools given
OL,9,Fthe uncertain future of LIPA, many
OL,10,Fparents told ITV News they would move
OL,11,Ftheir children back if the school is
OL,12,Fable to remain open.
OL,14,FMichelle Mooney - who moved her
OL,15,Fdaughter to another school when the
OL,16,Fpotential closure was announced - has
OL,17,Fnow moved her back to LIPA.
OL,19,FShe said: "When she got moved into the
OL,20,Fother school, there was no film
OL,21,Fstudies, no performing arts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
