OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,F"This is a performing arts school and
OL,8,Fthere's no other performing arts
OL,9,Fschools available to her."
OL,11,FMichelle still believes LIPA will stay
OL,12,Fopen, despite current plans for it to
OL,13,Fclose before the start of a new school
OL,14,Fyear in September 2026.
OL,16,FShe said: "If the court hears from the
OL,17,Fschool's point of view, the people who
OL,18,Factually attend LIPA, they will keep
OL,19,FLIPA open."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781046185
OL,3,CHigh Court to decide fate of
OL,4,Cperforming arts school ahead of
OL,5,Cpotential closure
OL,7,FThe Department of Education said:
OL,8,F"Declining pupil numbers and the
OL,9,Fschool's unsustainable financial
OL,10,Fposition has made it challenging for
OL,11,Fthe trust to continue to provide an
OL,12,Fenvironment that offers a high-quality
OL,13,Feducation."
OL,15,FThe legal team representing the
OL,16,Fparents have said that is a "false
OL,17,Ffinancial narrative."
OL,19,FBoth sides will be heard before the
OL,20,FHigh Court makes a final decision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
